This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and word embeddings, which are commonly studied in the computer science subfield of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves mathematical analysis and experimentation, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE).
